Jira Cloud Installation
1st we will check about how much it will cost of user licenses
•	Go to below URL
https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/pricing
Note : Data Center Enterprise edition cost less for license but Cloud cost between Standard and Premium

Cloud we have 3 options
•	Standard
•	Premium
•	Enterprise
How to download Jira cloud
•	Go to below URL
https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/pricing
•	Now select 10 users free
•	Now continue with google
•	Now it will show you work email address it will be your email
•	In Your site type the site name or get it from your manager
•	Now click on Agree
•	Now select software development
•	Now select devops
•	If you don’t want to give any questions you can skip as well
•	Select new to jira or you can skip
•	I am setting up jira for my software team
•	My team is experience with agile methodologies.
•	We spend our time working on fixing bug
•	We have flexible schedule to finish our work
•	Now click on next
•	Now enter the project name
•	Now click on create
•	Now click on skip this now
•	Now the jira installation is completed.
